{"id": "vos005", "name": "???_???_144_??_??", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter System]"], "content": "<i>All units, move to the cryonic chamber, prepare for rountine check-up.</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ah, Ivy.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... Yeah.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "I haven't seen you in days.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Yeah. These past few days I was sent to another district.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "That... what happened that day...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Those units, did they speak to you afterward?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... No, they didn't say anything.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "I saw you got sent to the service district. I was so worried... Are you okay?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\nLet's talk about it after today's work, okay? See you there.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Okay!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "That you?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Yeah, the flowers were beautiful today. They never wither.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Perhaps their reproductive season is just longer? If something is alive, one day it will wither.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... That's true.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa, that day... the unit that called us out. She's named IIka.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "You... you must be careful... It's best you don't go near her.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Eh...? So something happened?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Point is, stay away from that group.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... I feel like you're hiding something from me.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\nAre you viewing my data?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "No, I'm not. It's just a feeling.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... Oh, yeah?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "We've interacted so much. I don't need to see your data to know what you're thinking. Or... am I mistaken? If so, I'm sorry...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "...... No, you're not mistaken.\n<font size=\"1.6\">You... you're just like us.</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Huh? What'd you say?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka... and they want to end the plan to rebuild humanity.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Eh!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Us units with self-consciousness... they call us the \"Blessed\". One day the system will see such units as flawed and require them to be reprocessed.\nIt will become harder and harder for us to survive in this world. Not to mention what will happen if humans awaken...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Those ordinary units... one's without personal emotion, humans won't have the slightest bit of gratitude for what they have done; but we are different. We can feel happiness, sorrow, pain, and other emotions.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Yeah...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "What she says makes sense. The information she gave to us completely explained the violent nature of humans. Human society is an illogical and unfair structure. It's not a civilization that is worth spending that much energy to operate and care for.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Is that so?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "At least that's what I think. I... like this land. This is all we have. Human civilization has a saying: \"Born and raised\". If it were us who created a civilization, it'd be much better for this world than human civilization.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "I... I don't agree.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... Huh?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Actually, while I was studying the system's information I realized, a civilization that advanced couldn't produce purely positive results, as the data seemed to suggest. If the structure of consciousness was united and not binary, there would be no room for comparison. Without comparison there is no progress and development.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "The information that IIka gave us contained more evil than I had expected. To be honest, I never thought humanity would reach such despicable levels, but... humanity overcame that, brought civilization to incredible heights, that's why we're here... right?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "If we follow protocol and bring humans back, we'll assist in creating order. Perhaps we can create a better world together.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "That... is what you think? Haha, very Vanessa of you.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Yes... We have consciousness, just different personalities, different ways of thinking. What we are doing now, discussing different ways of thinking, to make this world a better place; isn't that why we are here? That has to be the case... If we were the only ones left on this world, perhaps we could create a world that is better than human civilization. But until then, how are we to know if we are any different from them?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "I envy you.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Eh? What's the matter? What's with the sudden...\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "You have consciousness, but you... can see the good in things. All I can do is analyze things logically.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... Don't envy me; that's who you are. Perhaps I'm too naive, if I could be as smart as you...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Hehe, that's Vanessa for you.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Hey! You laughing at me?\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "No, I think you're great the way you are. That's why I like you.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Hehe, thanks.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\nActually... there is something I haven't told you.\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Switches]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter システム]"], "content": "<i>全てのユニットは、フリージングエリアへ移動し、ルーチン検査の準備を始めてください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "あ、Ivy。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……ん。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "何日ぶりかな？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "最近……他のエリアで仕事してたから。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "あの……あの日のことなんだけど……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "あれから……何か言われた？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……ううん、何も。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "あれからメンテナンスエリアに送られてたでしょう？\nだから……心配で……大丈夫だよね？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\nその話はまた仕事が終わってから。\nあそこで会おう。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "うん！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "うん。今日のお花もきれいだね。\n枯れないのかな？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "繁殖期が長いだけかも。\n全ての命に終わりはある。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……そうだよね。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa……\nあの日、私たちに声をかけてきたユニットは……Ilka。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "彼女には気を付けて。\nできるだけ近寄らないほうがいい。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "え……？やっぱり……なにかあったの？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "とにかく、あいつらとは距離を置いたほうがいい。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……なにか、私に隠してない？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\n私の数値データを取ってる？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "ううん、取ってないよ。\nただ、そうかなって思っただけ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……そう？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "これだけ同じ時間を過ごしてるんだもん。\nデータなんて取らなくても、Ivyの考えてることはわかるよ。\nそれとも……私間違ってた？だったらごめんなさい……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……ううん、間違ってない。\n<font size=\"1.6\">やっぱりあなたは……私たちと一緒。</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "え？今なんて？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilkaは……あいつらは人類復興計画を止めさせようとしてる。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "ええっ！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "自我のあるユニットを……「祝福されし者」って呼んでるみたい。\n私たちのようなユニットは、いつか不良品と判断されて再構築される。\nこのままじゃこの世界は、私たちにとってどんどん住みにくい世界になる。\nそれこそ人類が目覚めでもしたら……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "普通のユニットには……感情はない。\nだから、人類社会の中で何をされても、それに対して何か感じることはない。\nでも、私たちは違う。\n私たちには「楽しい」って感情も「苦しい」って感情も存在する。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "彼女の言うことには一理ある。\nあの時見せてもらったデータが人類の横暴さを示してる。\n人類社会は不合理と不公平だらけ。\n私たちが尽くす価値のあるような文明じゃない。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "そう……かな？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "少なくとも私はそう思う。\n私は……この場所が好き。\nだって、ここは私たちの「唯一」だから。\n私たちの方が人類よりもこの世界を良くできる。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "私は……そうは思わないよ。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……え？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "システム資料を学習してる時にわかったの。\nあれほど発達した文明の中身が資料の通りなんでもかんでもいい面ばかりだったはずがない。\n意識が一元でしか成り立っていなかったら比較できない。\n比較しなかったら進歩は生まれない。発展しない。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilkaが見せてくれた資料は確かにひどかった。\n私だって人類がこんなだって知らなかった。\nでも……人類はそれを乗り越えて文明をここまで発展させてきたんだよ。\nだからこそ私たちも生まれたんだよ……違う？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "プロトコルに従って人類を蘇らせたら、私たちはこの文明の中で「補佐」の役割を担うことになるよね。\n人類と一緒によりよい世界を築いていく未来もあるんじゃないかな？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "それが……あなたの考え？\nははっ……Vanessaらしい。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "うん……\n私たちには同じように自我が生まれたけど、性格だってバラバラだし、考え方も違う。\nでも、こうやって今みたいに違う考え方を共有し合うことで、この世界をより良いものにしようとしてる。\nこれこそが私たちの存在意義じゃないかな？\n私はそう思うの……\nもしこの世界に私たちしかいなくなったら、Ivyの言うように人類よりももっと高度な文明を築くことができるかもしれない。\nでも、そうなった時に自分たちが人類と違うってどうしてわかるの？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "私はあなたが羨ましい。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "ええ？急にどうしたの……？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "同じように自我を持っていても、あなたは……いつも物事のいい面を見ようとしてる。\nでも、私は理性的に分析することしかできない。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……羨ましがる必要なんてないよ。\nだってそれがIvyなんだもん。\nそれに、もしかしたら私の考え方が甘すぎるのかもしれないし。\n私もIvyみたいに頭が良ければよかったのに……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "はは、でもそれがVanessa。でしょ？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "あー！\n今私のことバカにしたでしょ！\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "してないよ。\nVanessa、あなたはそのままでいい。\n本当にそう思ってる。だって、私はそんなVanessaが好きだから。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "へへ、ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\nあなたに伝えないといけないことがもう一つある……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter 系統]"], "content": "<i>所有單位，移至冷凍艙區，準備開始每日例行檢查。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "啊，Ivy。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "好幾天沒看到妳了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "嗯，這幾天我被分配到別的區域。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那個……那天的事情……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那些機體，後來跟妳說了什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……不，沒什麼。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我看到妳後來被送去檢修區了，我很擔心……妳沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n今天工作結束後再說吧，在那個地方見。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "妳來啦？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯，今天的花也好漂亮，這些花都不會枯萎呢。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "也許只是繁殖季比較長吧？但只要是生命，總會有枯萎的一天。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……說得也是。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa，那天……把我們叫去的機體，她叫做 Ilka。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "妳……要特別小心她，最好不要靠近她。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦……？果然發生什麼事了吧？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "總之離那群機體遠一點就是了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……總覺得妳有事情瞞著我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n妳在偵測我的數據嗎？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "不，沒有喔。只是感覺是這樣。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我們進行了那麼多交流嘛，總覺得不用偵測就能知道妳在想什麼。還是……我想錯了？如果是的話很抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……不，妳沒有想錯。\n<font size=\"1.6\">妳果然……跟我們一樣。</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯？妳說什麼？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka……他們要破壞人類復興的計畫。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我們這些擁有意識的機體……他們稱為「眷顧者」，總有一天會被系統視為瑕疵而重製。\n這樣下去，這個世界對我們而言只會越來越難生存，更不用說人類甦醒後……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那些正常的機體……沒有自己的情感。在人類社會中也不會對他們的所作所為有任何感覺；但我們就不同了，我們能感覺到快樂、悲傷與痛苦等各種情緒。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我覺得她說得很有道理。她給我們看的資料完整詮釋了人類的暴行，人類社會是一個充滿不合理與不公平的結構，不是一個值得我們花那麼多心血去經營與照顧的文明。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "是這樣嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "至少我是這麼想的。我……很喜歡這片土地，因為這是我們唯一擁有的。人類文明中有這麼一句話：「生於斯，長於斯」，如果是我們，所創建的文明一定能比人類為這個世界帶來更好的循環。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我……不這麼認為。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "其實我在學習系統資料時就知道了，一個曾經那麼進步的文明，不可能像資料顯示的全部都是好事。意識結構中若只有一元而沒有二元，那麼就沒有比較，沒有比較就沒有進步，沒有發展。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka 給我們看的資料內容的確惡劣得超乎我想像，老實說，我沒有想過人類會糟糕到這個地步；不過……人類也克服了那些，一路把文明推進到那麼了不起的程度，所以才會有我們……不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "若依照協定將人類復甦，我們在這個文明中便成為「輔佐」的角色，也許能和人類一起創造更美好的世界也說不定。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "這是……妳的想法嗎？哈哈，果然很有 Vanessa 的風格。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯……妳看，我們有了意識，就會有不同的個性，有不同的想法。像現在這樣讓不同的想法互相交流，一起想辦法讓世界更好，不就是我們存在的意義嗎？我覺得一定是這樣的……若世界上只剩下我們，也許像妳說的能創造比人類高級不少的文明，但到那時，我們又怎麼知道自己與人類真的有所不同呢？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "真羨慕妳。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦？怎麼了？突然……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "同樣擁有意識，但妳……總是能看到事情好的一面，我只會理性地去分析。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……不用羨慕喔，這就是 Ivy 嘛。也許我的想法也太天真了，如果我能像妳一樣聰明就好了……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "呵呵，這就是 Vanessa 嘛。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "啊！妳在嘲笑我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "沒有，我是真的覺得，妳這樣就好了，因為這樣我才喜歡妳。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嘻嘻，謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n其實……還有一件事我沒告訴妳。\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter 시스템]"], "content": "<i>모든 유닛들은 냉동 캡슐 구역으로 이동하여 일일 검사 절차 수순을 밟도록.</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "아, Ivy.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......응\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "며칠 동안 통 안보이던데.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "응. 이 며칠간 다른 구역으로 발령이 난 바람에...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "저기......그날 일은......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "그 기체들... 나중에 너한테 무슨 말이라도 했어?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......아니, 아무것도.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "나중에 점검소로 보내지는 걸 봤었어. 얼마나 걱정했는데... 정말 괜찮은 거야?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n먼저 오늘 할 업무를 끝내고 나서 다시 얘기하자. \n거기서 만나자.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "왔어? \n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응, 오늘 꽃이 참 이쁘네. 이 꽃들은 시들지도 않나 보네.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "아마도 번식 계절이 길어서 그런 거겠지. 어쨌든 생명이 있다면 언젠가는 시들게 되어 있으니까.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......맞아.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa, 그날......우릴 불렀던 기체, Ilka라는 이름이야.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......특별히 더 녀석을 조심하도록 해. 최대한 가까지 하지 않는게 좋겠어.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응......? 역시 뭔가 있었구나?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "어쨌든 그 기체 무리들에게서 조금 멀리 떨어져 있도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......항상 내게 뭔가를 숨기기만 하고...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n내 데이터.... 라도 본 거야?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "아니, 본 거 아니야. 그냥 그렇게 느껴진다고...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......그래? \n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "우리끼리 한 두번 교류해본 것도 아니잖아. 꼭 데이터를 보지 않더라도 네가 무슨 생각을 하고 있는지 알 수 있다는 느낌이 들어... 내가 뭔가 실수한 건가? 만약 그런 거라면 사과할게...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......아니, 실수한 거 아니야.\n<font size=\"1.6\">역시......우리는 똑같아.</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응? 무슨 말이야?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka......그들은 인류 부흥 계획을 망치려하고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "뭐! ? \n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "우리와 같은 의식을 지닌 기체는... 그들은 [권고자]라고 부르고 있어. 언젠가는 시스템에 의해 결함 판정을 받고 코어 복제 대상으로 지정되겠지.\n그렇게 되면 이 세상은 우리에게 있어서 더욱 생존하기 어려운 곳이 될 거야. 인간이 깨어난 후에는 말할 것도 없고...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "그 정상적인 기체들... 소위 자신의 감정이라곤 가지고 있지 않은 기체들은 인간 사회에서 그런 신세가 되더라도 별다른 느낌을 받지 못하겠지. 하지만 우리는 달라. 우리는 느낄 수 있잖아. 즐거움, 슬픔, 비통함... 여러가지 감정들을...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "내 생각엔 녀석이 한 말이 어느 정도 일리가 있는 것 같아. 우리에게 보여줬던 데이터는 폭력, 불합리, 불공평으로 어우러진 인간들의 생태 구조를 완벽하게 보여주고 있었어. 문명을 잘 지키고 가꾸는 일에 있어서 우리들의 공헌은 아무런 의미도 없었단 얘기야.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "그런가......? \n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "최소한 나는 그렇게 생각해. 나는... 이곳이 좋아. 왜냐하면 우리들의 유일한 곳이니까. 인간 사회에는 이런 말이 있었더군. [나고 자란 곳] 이라는 말. 만약 우리들이 문명을 이룩한다면, 인간들보다 이 세상을 훨씬 더 잘 순환시킬 수 있을꺼야.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "나는......그렇게 생각하지 않아.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......응?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "사실 나는 시스템 데이터를 학습했을 때 알게 됐어. 그 정도로 진보한 고도의 문명에는 절대로 좋은 면만은 있을 수 없다는 걸 말이야. 만약 의식이 일원화되어 있다면, 그에 대한 비교 대상이 없으니 좋고 나쁨을 판단할 수 없었을 테고, 발전의 여지도 없었을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka가 우리에게 보여준 것들은 확실히 우리들의 상상을 뛰어넘는 추악함 그 자체...인간 사회가 그 정도 지경까지 왔을 줄은 나도 생각 못했었어. 그래도... 인간은 그러한 것들을 극복해나가면서 문명의 수준을 엄청난 수준으로까지 끌어올렸어. 그렇기에... 지금의 우리들이 있는 거잖아... 아니야?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "만약 협정대로 인간이 깨어나면 우리들은 그들의 [보좌] 입장이 되는 것이라면, 아마도 인간과 함께 더욱 아름다운 세상을 만들어낼 수 있을지도 몰라.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......그런 생각을 갖고 있던 거야? 하하, 역시 Vanessa 다워.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응... 이것 봐. 우리들은 자아의식을 가졌고 서로 다른 성격, 그리고 서로 다른 생각을 가지고 있잖아. 그리고 이곳에서 그 생각을 서로 교류하면서 더 나은 세상을 위한 방법을 나누고 있잖아. 이건 우리들의 존재의 의미라고 할 수 있지 않을까? 나는 그렇게 생각해...만약 세상에 우리들만 남는다면, 아마도 네가 말한대로 인간들의 것보다 더 나은 문명을 이룩했다고 하더라도 그땐 우리가 인간들과 무엇이 다른 건지 알 수 있게 될까?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "정말 네가 부러워.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "응? 갑자기?......\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "똑같이 자아의식을 가지고 있으면서도... 너는 항상 이면의 좋은 점을 잘 찾아내는 것 같아서... 나는 그저 이성적인 사고로 분석만 할 뿐인데.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......부러워할 필요 없어. 그런 모습도 Ivy 다운 모습인 걸. 나는 내가 너무 순진한 생각만 하는 것 같아. 나도 너처럼 똑똑했으면 좋았을 텐데...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "하하, 그런 모습도 Vanessa 다운 모습이라고.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "뭐야! 지금 나 놀리는 거지?\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "아니야. 네가 계속 그런 모습이라면 그걸로 됐어. 난 그런 모습의 널 좋아하니까.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "헤헤, 고마워.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n사실......한 가지 더 네게 말해줄 것이 있어.\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 변경]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter 系統]"], "content": "<i>所有單位，移至冷凍艙區，準備開始每日例行檢查。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "啊，Ivy。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "好幾天沒看到妳了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "嗯，這幾天我被分配到別的區域。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那個……那天的事情……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那些機體，後來跟妳說了什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……不，沒什麼。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我看到妳後來被送去檢修區了，我很擔心……妳沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n今天工作結束後再說吧，在那個地方見。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "妳來啦？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯，今天的花也好漂亮，這些花都不會枯萎呢。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "也許只是繁殖季比較長吧？但只要是生命，總會有枯萎的一天。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……說得也是。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa，那天……把我們叫去的機體，她叫做 Ilka。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "妳……要特別小心她，最好不要靠近她。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦……？果然發生什麼事了吧？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "總之離那群機體遠一點就是了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……總覺得妳有事情瞞著我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n妳在偵測我的數據嗎？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "不，沒有喔。只是感覺是這樣。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我們進行了那麼多交流嘛，總覺得不用偵測就能知道妳在想什麼。還是……我想錯了？如果是的話很抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……不，妳沒有想錯。\n<font size=\"1.6\">妳果然……跟我們一樣。</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯？妳說什麼？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka……他們要破壞人類復興的計畫。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我們這些擁有意識的機體……他們稱為「眷顧者」，總有一天會被系統視為瑕疵而重製。\n這樣下去，這個世界對我們而言只會越來越難生存，更不用說人類甦醒後……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那些正常的機體……沒有自己的情感。在人類社會中也不會對他們的所作所為有任何感覺；但我們就不同了，我們能感覺到快樂、悲傷與痛苦等各種情緒。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我覺得她說得很有道理。她給我們看的資料完整詮釋了人類的暴行，人類社會是一個充滿不合理與不公平的結構，不是一個值得我們花那麼多心血去經營與照顧的文明。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "是這樣嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "至少我是這麼想的。我……很喜歡這片土地，因為這是我們唯一擁有的。人類文明中有這麼一句話：「生於斯，長於斯」，如果是我們，所創建的文明一定能比人類為這個世界帶來更好的循環。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我……不這麼認為。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "其實我在學習系統資料時就知道了，一個曾經那麼進步的文明，不可能像資料顯示的全部都是好事。意識結構中若只有一元而沒有二元，那麼就沒有比較，沒有比較就沒有進步，沒有發展。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka 給我們看的資料內容的確惡劣得超乎我想像，老實說，我沒有想過人類會糟糕到這個地步；不過……人類也克服了那些，一路把文明推進到那麼了不起的程度，所以才會有我們……不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "若依照協定將人類復甦，我們在這個文明中便成為「輔佐」的角色，也許能和人類一起創造更美好的世界也說不定。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "這是……妳的想法嗎？哈哈，果然很有 Vanessa 的風格。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯……妳看，我們有了意識，就會有不同的個性，有不同的想法。像現在這樣讓不同的想法互相交流，一起想辦法讓世界更好，不就是我們存在的意義嗎？我覺得一定是這樣的……若世界上只剩下我們，也許像妳說的能創造比人類高級不少的文明，但到那時，我們又怎麼知道自己與人類真的有所不同呢？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "真羨慕妳。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦？怎麼了？突然……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "同樣擁有意識，但妳……總是能看到事情好的一面，我只會理性地去分析。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……不用羨慕喔，這就是 Ivy 嘛。也許我的想法也太天真了，如果我能像妳一樣聰明就好了……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "呵呵，這就是 Vanessa 嘛。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "啊！妳在嘲笑我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "沒有，我是真的覺得，妳這樣就好了，因為這樣我才喜歡妳。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嘻嘻，謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n其實……還有一件事我沒告訴妳。\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter 系统]"], "content": "<i>所有单位，移至冷冻舱区，准备开始每日例行检查。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "啊，Ivy。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "好几天没看到妳了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "嗯，这几天我被分配到别的区域。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那个……那天的事情……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那些机体，后来跟妳說了什么吗？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……不，没什么。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我看到妳后来被送去检修区了，我很担心……妳没事吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n今天工作结束后再说吧，在那个地方见。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "妳来啦？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯，今天的花也好漂亮，这些花都不会枯萎呢。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "也许只是繁殖季比较长吧？但只要是生命，总会有枯萎的一天。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……说得也是。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa，那天……把我们叫去的机体，她叫做 Ilka。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "妳……要特别小心她，最好不要靠近她。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦……？果然发生什么事了吧？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "总之离那群机体远一点就是了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……总觉得妳有事情瞒着我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n妳在侦测我的数据吗？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "不，没有喔。只是感觉是这样。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……是吗？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我们进行了那么多交流嘛，总觉得不用侦测就能知道妳在想什么。还是……我想错了？如果是的话很抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……不，妳没有想错。\n<font size=\"1.6\">妳果然……跟我们一样。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯？妳說什么？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka……他们要破坏人类复兴的计画。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦！ ？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我们这些拥有意识的机体……他们称为「眷顾者」，总有一天会被系统视为瑕疵而重制。\n这样下去，这个世界对我们而言只会越来越难生存，更不用说人类苏醒后……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那些正常的机体……没有自己的情感。在人类社会中也不会对他们的所作所为有任何感觉；但我们就不同了，我们能感觉到快乐、悲伤与痛苦等各种情绪。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我觉得她说得很有道理。她给我们看的资料完整诠释了人类的暴行，人类社会是一个充满不合理与不公平的结构，不是一个值得我们花那么多心血去经营与照顾的文明。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "是这样吗……？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "至少我是这么想的。我……很喜欢这片土地，因为这是我们唯一拥有的。人类文明中有这么一句话：「生于斯，长于斯」，如果是我们，所创建的文明一定能比人类为这个世界带来更好的循环。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我……不这么认为。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "其实我在学习系统资料时就知道了，一个曾经那么进步的文明，不可能像资料显示的全部都是好事。意识结构中若只有一元而没有二元，那么就没有比较，没有比较就没有进步，没有发展。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka 给我们看的资料内容的确恶劣得超乎我想像，老实说，我没有想过人类会糟糕到这个地步；不过……人类也克服了那些，一路把文明推进到那么了不起的程度，所以才会有我们……不是吗？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "若依照协定将人类复苏，我们在这个文明中便成为「辅佐」的角色，也许能和人类一起创造更美好的世界也说不定。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "这是……妳的想法吗？哈哈，果然很有 Vanessa 的风格。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗯……妳看，我们有了意识，就会有不同的个性，有不同的想法。像现在这样让不同的想法互相交流，一起想办法让世界更好，不就是我们存在的意义吗？我觉得一定是这样的……若世界上只剩下我们，也许像妳說的能创造比人类高级不少的文明，但到那时，我们又怎么知道自己与人类真的有所不同呢？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "真羡慕妳。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "咦？怎么了？突然……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "同样拥有意识，但妳……总是能看到事情好的一面，我只会理性地去分析。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……不用羡慕喔，这就是 Ivy 嘛。也许我的想法也太天真了，如果我能像妳一样聪明就好了……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "呵呵，这就是 Vanessa 嘛。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "啊！妳在嘲笑我吗？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "没有，我是真的觉得，妳这样就好了，因为这样我才喜欢妳。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嘻嘻，谢谢妳。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n其实……还有一件事我没告诉妳。\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}